The paper deals with image parsing, which is a task related to computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes an adaptive nonparametric approach, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves feature extraction and contextual smoothing, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper involves retrieval sets and similarity matching, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
